data.description: Welcome Home. Come view this beautiful 4 bedroom 2.5 bathroom home located in Blue Springs Villas. This home features an upgraded eat in kitchen with spacious vaulted ceilings. The Master Bedroom is located downstairs with a beautiful oversized jacuzzi style tub and walk in shower.  There is also a dining area that sits closely to the screened in back porch. Upstairs you will find the remaining 3 spacious bedrooms, with a closed in laundry downstairs.  The appliances include, Refrigerator and dishwasher with a washing machine and dryer. This home sits on a cul-de-sac which features a playground area and walk-about. Close and convenient to downtown Orange City and the park and Library,  just minutes away from I-4 and 17-92. (New Roof to be installed with full offer price of $375,000)
